    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2659275533" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2659275533" />
    <a title="Dannii Elle" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/44487975-dannii-elle"><img alt="Dannii Elle" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1623521403p2/44487975.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2659275533?book_show_action=true">Feb 17, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dannii Elle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dannii Elle" href="/user/show/44487975-dannii-elle">Dannii Elle</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780099532927" href="/book/show/6586236-the-silence-of-the-lambs">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44487975-dannii-elle?shelf=crime-creations">crime-creations</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44487975-dannii-elle?shelf=adult-books-read">adult-books-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44487975-dannii-elle?shelf=mysterious-miasmas">mysterious-miasmas</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44487975-dannii-elle?shelf=thriven-thrillers">thriven-thrillers</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2659275533" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7493090635751075926">Actual rating 4.5/5 stars. This is the second instalment in the Hannibal Lecter series.<br/><br/>I had watched the movie adaptations multiple times before beginning the original books but found them no less shocking, blood-soaked, twisted, and unputdownable for that. This and <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/32418.Hannibal__Hannibal_Lecter___3_' title='Hannibal (Hannibal Lecter, #3) by Thomas Harris' rel='nofollow noopener'>Hannibal</a> were by far my favourite two of the four available in the series. They are also both the two that deal most directly with Hannibal&apos;s twisted deviances.</span>
  <span id="freeText7493090635751075926" style="display:none">Actual rating 4.5/5 stars. This is the second instalment in the Hannibal Lecter series.<br /><br />I had watched the movie adaptations multiple times before beginning the original books but found them no less shocking, blood-soaked, twisted, and unputdownable for that. This and <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/32418.Hannibal__Hannibal_Lecter___3_" title="Hannibal (Hannibal Lecter, #3) by Thomas Harris" rel="nofollow noopener">Hannibal</a> were by far my favourite two of the four available in the series. They are also both the two that deal most directly with Hannibal's twisted deviances.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7493090635751075926" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


